      "text": "and give me back my fur"
    },
    {
      "start": 672.7,
      "end": 674.84,
      "text": "I think you're trying to say"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.84,
      "end": 676.46,
      "text": "that the reason I can see you"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.46,
      "end": 678.88,
      "text": "is because I have a little piece of your fur"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.88,
      "end": 681.58,
      "text": "네, 잘 들리셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 682.58,
      "end": 683.38,
      "text": "송연서님께서"
    },
    {
      "start": 683.38,
      "end": 686.16,
      "text": "언제 들어도 유쾌한 크리스님"
    },
    {
      "start": 686.16,
      "end": 688.04,
      "text": "이번 주도 수고 많으셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.04,
      "end": 689.9,
      "text": "주말 잘 보내시고"
    },
    {
      "start": 689.9,
      "end": 691.76,
      "text": "다음 주에 봐요 하셨어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.76,
      "end": 693.3,
      "text": "Thanks, I'll see you next week"
    }
  ]
}